N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 341.21 - Rules of procedure

State Regulations

Procedures at the meetings of the student assembly, the
executive committee or other duly constituted committees shall be governed by

Robert's Rules of Order, except as otherwise provided by this Part or the
bylaws. Notes
